@startuml

[*] --> State1
State1 : User Starts Program
State1 --> State2 : User clicks "Start Recording"
State2 : Recording in Progress, Audio being transcribed, Live text displayed in UI
State2 --> State3 : User clicks "Stop Recording"
State3 : Recording Stopped, Final transcription sent to AI for cleanup
State4 --> State2 : User can record again to append text
State3 --> State4 : Processing complete, Cleaned notes displayed in UI
State4 : Cleaned notes displayed in UI, Option to save notes to .txt file
State4 --> State5 : User clicks "Save Notes"
State5 : Cleaned notes saved to .txt file of user choosing



@enduml